projects.title: TweetCraze
projects.about: TweetCraze enables business to engage with their customers on Twitter through AI. TweetCraze can send message, reply to messages , tweet and comment on tweets on your behalf.

projects.title: Orami
projects.about: A simply fast ORM framework for Sqlite3 suitable for small to mid-sized projects. I have used it in several social media bot projects. I was developed while working on ChatBot
